msgstr "你成功击退了海盗船。你注意到海盗正在撤退，看来超能族赢了。你迅速清理了战利品残骸。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_pirate.xml.append:363
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_pirate.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_LECTURE_MARKET_WIN_ZOLTAN\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "联系超能族和平大队。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_pirate.xml.append:365
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_pirate.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ZOLTAN_LECTURE_MARKET_WIN_ZOLTAN\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr "\"我们没有料到联邦的增援。我们非常感谢你们的帮助。按照超能族的习惯，我们现在欠了你们人情，将尽职尽责地偿还。\""

